MIPS: Malta: GIC IPIs may be used without MT

It's perfectly valid to use SMP on a non-MT CPU and use the GIC for
IPIs. Set them up conditional upon CONFIG_MIPS_GIC_IPI rather than
CONFIG_MIPS_MT_SMP.

